Dia. 01 Useless
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's dansu at 1 is a beginner's move. If White connects at 2, Black can't do anything else so his five stones are captured.
\par
